      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared using validation metric u_val per ASME V&V 20. Experimental uncertainty is ±12% (k=2); simulation uncertainty from Monte Carlo is ±9%. Mean prediction error is +14%, indicating a slight positive bias. Bias source is attributed to hemolysis model form but has not been formally decomposed. Achieved level 3 due to incomplete bias characterisation."
